          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/224.step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>baked risotto</strong> in bowls with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, season generously with <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>mint</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
